  "exercises": "<div class=\"pt-6 font-sans\">\n    <!-- Lesson Title -->\n    <div class=\"text-center px-4 mb-12\">\n        <h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-800\">Lesson 12: Practice Exercises</h1>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-lg text-sky-600 font-medium\">Let's practice using our algebraic shortcuts!</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Exercise 1 -->\n    <div class=\"exercise-container max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4 mb-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Exercise 1: Difference of Squares with an Integer</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4\">Simplify the expression:   <strong>(10 - √6)(10 + √6)</strong></p>\n        <button class=\"show-answer-button mt-4 bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-600 transition duration-300\">Show Answer</button>\n        <div class=\"answer-container mt-4 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Solving the Expression:</h4>\n            <div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 1:</strong> This matches the identity (a - b)(a + b) = a² - b², where a = 10 and b = √6.</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 2:</strong> Apply the identity: (10)² - (√6)².</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 3:</strong> Calculate each part: 100 - 6.</p>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 font-bold text-lg text-green-600\">Final Answer: 94</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- Exercise 2 -->\n    <div class=\"exercise-container max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4 mb-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Exercise 2: Squaring a Difference</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4\">Simplify the expression:   <strong>(√7 - √2)²</strong></p>\n        <button class=\"show-answer-button mt-4 bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-600 transition duration-300\">Show Answer</button>\n        <div class=\"answer-container mt-4 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Simplifying the Square:</h4>\n            <div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 1:</strong> This matches the identity (a - b)² = a² - 2ab + b², where a = √7 and b = √2.</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 2:</strong> Apply the identity: (√7)² - 2(√7)(√2) + (√2)².</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 3:</strong> Simplify each term: 7 - 2√(7×2) + 2.</p>\n                 <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 4:</strong> Combine the rational parts: 7 + 2 = 9.</p>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 font-bold text-lg text-green-600\">Final Answer: 9 - 2√14</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Exercise 3 -->\n    <div class=\"exercise-container max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4 mb-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Exercise 3: Find the Missing Piece</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4\">What expression should be multiplied by <strong>(√5 + 3)</strong> to get a rational number?</p>\n        <button class=\"show-answer-button mt-4 bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-600 transition duration-300\">Show Answer</button>\n        <div class=\"answer-container mt-4 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Finding the Conjugate:</h4>\n            <div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                <p class=\"mb-2\">To eliminate the square root and get a rational number, we need to use the difference of squares identity: (a+b)(a-b) = a²-b².</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\">We have the (a+b) part, which is (√5 + 3).</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\">Therefore, the missing piece is the (a-b) part, which is found by just flipping the sign in the middle.</p>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 font-bold text-lg text-green-600\">Final Answer: (√5 - 3)</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- Exercise 4 -->\n    <div class=\"exercise-container max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4 mb-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Exercise 4: Simplify the Radical</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4\">Simplify <strong>√50</strong> by finding the largest perfect square factor.</p>\n        <button class=\"show-answer-button mt-4 bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-600 transition duration-300\">Show Answer</button>\n        <div class=\"answer-container mt-4 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Simplifying the Radical:</h4>\n            <div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 1:</strong> We need to find factors of 50 where one of them is a perfect square (like 4, 9, 16, 25...).</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\">We can write 50 as <strong>25 × 2</strong>.</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\"><strong>Step 2:</strong> Use the identity √(ab) = √a × √b.</p>\n                <p class=\"font-mono text-lg ml-6 mt-1 text-gray-700\">√50 = √(25 × 2) = √25 × √2</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2 mt-2\"><strong>Step 3:</strong> Simplify the perfect square part.</p>\n                 <p class=\"font-mono text-lg ml-6 mt-1 text-gray-700\">√25 = 5</p>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 font-bold text-lg text-green-600\">Final Answer: 5√2</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- Exercise 5 -->\n    <div class=\"exercise-container max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4 mb-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Exercise 5: True or False?</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4\">Is the statement <strong>√(a+b) = √a + √b</strong> always true?</p>\n        <button class=\"show-answer-button mt-4 bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-600 transition duration-300\">Show Answer</button>\n        <div class=\"answer-container mt-4 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Checking the Statement:</h4>\n            <div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                <p class=\"mb-2\">To check if a statement is false, we just need one counterexample. Let's pick simple values for a and b.</p>\n                <p class=\"mb-2\">Let a = 9 and b = 16.</p>\n                 <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-3\">\n                    <li><strong>Left side:</strong> √(a+b) = √(9+16) = √25 = 5.</li>\n                    <li><strong>Right side:</strong> √a + √b = √9 + √16 = 3 + 4 = 7.</li>\n                </ul>\n                <p class=\"mt-2\">Since 5 is not equal to 7, the statement is not always true.</p>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 font-bold text-lg text-red-600\">Final Answer: False.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <!-- Exercise 6 -->\n    <div class=\"exercise-container max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4 mb-8\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2\">Exercise 6: Multiplication Practice</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4\">Simplify the expression:   <strong>(3 - √2)(4 + √2)</strong></p>\n        <button class=\"show-answer-button mt-4 bg-sky-500 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-600 transition duration-300\">Show Answer</button>\n        <div class=\"answer-container mt-4 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg\">\n            <h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2\">Simplifying the Product:</h4>\n            <div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed\">\n                <p class=\"mb-2\">We use the FOIL method to multiply the terms.</p>\n                <ul class=\"list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-2 font-mono\">\n                    <li><strong>F</strong>irst: 3 × 4 = 12</li>\n                    <li><strong>O</strong>uter: 3 × √2 = 3√2</li>\n                    <li><strong>I</strong>nner: -√2 × 4 = -4√2</li>\n                    <li><strong>L</strong>ast: -√2 × √2 = -2</li>\n                </ul>\n                 <p class=\"mb-2 mt-2\">Combine all the parts: 12 + 3√2 - 4√2 - 2.</p>\n                 <p class=\"mb-2 mt-2\">Now, group and combine the like terms:</p>\n                 <p class=\"font-mono text-lg ml-6 mt-1 text-gray-700\">(12 - 2) + (3√2 - 4√2) = 10 - 1√2</p>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"mt-4 font-bold text-lg text-green-600\">Final Answer: 10 - √2</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n</div>\n<!--end-of-code-block-->",
